The StarPortal has taken you from the hells of Miasma to a paradise of sparkling waves and sun-soaked beaches--but this heavenly allure hides a deadly enemy and a hellish new weapon. Schultz remains free, but his messages have stopped, and royalist Hadeans are hot on his trail. Your only hope is to contact Prince Thanatos's rebels and ask them to help you find Schultz before his time runs out.